WEBVTT

00:03.271 --> 00:05.650
My name is Barnabas Collins.

00:06.400 --> 00:09.755
Two centuries ago, I made Collinwood my home.

00:10.147 --> 00:10.653
My love.

00:11.416 --> 00:16.463
Until a jealous witch cursed me, condemning me to the shadow...

00:16.553 --> 00:17.927
What have you done?

00:18.188 --> 00:19.391
...for all time.

00:23.639 --> 00:24.820
What the hell is this?

00:25.087 --> 00:25.869
He's coming.

00:27.113 --> 00:27.977
He's coming.

00:31.533 --> 00:33.059
Hear me, future dweller.

00:33.298 --> 00:34.132
What is the year?

00:34.397 --> 00:35.565
1972.

00:35.971 --> 00:37.561
1972.

00:40.705 --> 00:42.059
My beloved Collinwood.

00:42.260 --> 00:43.217
The Collins family.

00:43.395 --> 00:44.311
Who the hell is this?

00:44.452 --> 00:45.723
I am a vampire, madam.

00:45.919 --> 00:46.059
Yeah.

00:47.870 --> 00:49.707
He's not staying with us forever, is he?

00:49.871 --> 00:50.523
I like him.

00:52.121 --> 00:54.151
Welcome home, Barnabas Collins.

00:54.240 --> 00:55.771
How soon can the horses be ready?

00:56.075 --> 00:57.271
We don't have horses.

00:58.095 --> 00:58.867
We have a Chevy.

01:03.201 --> 01:04.674
What sorcery is this?

01:06.314 --> 01:08.501
Reveal yourself, tiny songstress!

01:10.807 --> 01:12.849
Hello, Barnabas. Remember me?

01:13.059 --> 01:15.544
Witch! You cursed me to be this hideous creature.

01:15.697 --> 01:19.439
You may strategically place your wonderful lips upon my posterior and kiss it repeatedly.

01:25.645 --> 01:26.375
Is she for real?

01:26.522 --> 01:27.085
Indeed.

01:30.202 --> 01:33.519
If I can't have you, I'll destroy you. And your family.

01:35.839 --> 01:36.339
Missed me.

01:41.829 --> 01:44.696
I shall restore the family business to its former glory.

01:45.488 --> 01:47.389
Burn baby, burn!

01:48.647 --> 01:51.739
Fight on, Barnabas. Fight on for us.

01:51.853 --> 01:53.954
And fight I shall.

02:01.493 --> 02:02.870
Are you stoned or something?

02:03.031 --> 02:04.638
They tried stoning me, my dear.

02:05.569 --> 02:06.373
It did not work.

